You have a few gifts no doubt, but some are there to support the others.

E.g. I have always had a love for clothes! I just loved to be suited & booted & at a point I thought I was called into fashion. Thank God it was a brief moment! You know how I knew I wasn't called? There were several pointers but a major one was that I had NO ORIGINAL THOUGHTS IN THAT AREA! I would later find out that my love for fashion was supposed to support my other MAJOR GIFTS.
